description: This file defines the APIs for device prioritization in the TestDiagnostics Data Model Library, including function declarations to get and set parameter string values related to device control.

methods.name: DscpControl_GetParamStringValue
methods.description: Retrieves the string value of a specified parameter for device control.

methods.name: DscpControl_SetParamStringValue
methods.description: Sets the string value of a specified parameter for device control.
